prompts.prompt: Create a Swift app named 'Wetact Scanner' that allows users to scan a room using their iPhone and generates a 3D file of the scanned area. The app should also automatically place furniture in the house based on what it has detected during the scan. Utilize Apple's RoomPlan API as described in the link https://developer.apple.com/documentation/roomplan/providing_custom_models_for_captured_rooms_and_structure_exports to facilitate this functionality.
